lead_paragraph: Dwyane Wade scored 27 points and the Miami Heat beat the Phoenix Suns for the 11th straight time with a 103-95 victory Friday night.

headline.print_headline: Wade Scores 27, Heat Win as Dragic, Green Return to Phoenix
